{"text": " Welcome to the three-minute guided meditation training by All Here. We will now begin five rounds consisting of three minutes each with one minute pause in between. We shall begin the first round in ten seconds. Round one. Visualize the cosmic sky. Look at the night sky. See the stars, look at the darkness. See the cosmic sky. Allow the stars to move closer to you. And look at the dark space between the stars. Look at the darkness. Allow the stars to shift away as you move towards darkness. See the dark space. Look at the darkness, approaching your face. Look at the dark. And round one. And round one. Round two. Visualize the full moon inside your chest. Look at the full moon inside you. The moon and the moonlight, lighting of your chest. The moon might, lighting of your stomach. Your lungs, your shoulders, coming upward through your throat. Look at the shining moon inside you. See the full moon. The full moon inside your chest. The moon and the moonlight. Beaming through your chest, lighting of your throat. And round two. Round three. Now visualize a star in your belly right in the center of gravity. Look at the shining star, deep in your belly. Surrounded by darkness of the belly. Sense the star and the starlight emanating from your center. Lighting up through your body, starlight shining vertically up to the center. Look at the shining star. Keep looking. The star, the starlight. Look at the shining star, deep in your belly. And round three. Now visualize a star in your belly. Surrounded by darkness of the belly. Surrounded by darkness of the belly. The increasing and expanding darkness starts to cover the starlight. As the star fades away into the darkness. Look at the darkness surrounding the center of gravity. Gaze at the darkness of the belly. Look at the space of dark. Deep in the belly. Deep in the belly. Continue to look at the dark in the belly. End of round four. End of round four. Round five. Now visualize the cosmic sky in front of you. Gaze at stars then at the darkness. Move closer to the stars. As they disappear away. You move beyond stars towards darkness. See the deep dark beyond all planets. The darkness in front of you. The darkness approaching to your face. Touch the darkness. Stay in the dark. End of round five. Round six. Visualize a single star in the dark sky. Look at the shining star star starlight coming in any direction. See how the star is moving closer to you, increasing in size, and forming into an image of sun in front of you. Look at the sun and the sunlight shining onto your face, onto your body, shining through. The sun is moving closer. The giant sun in front of you, the light piercing through your body as you enter the space of sun. Enter the sunlight, lighting on the entire space. You absorb into the sun. You merge into the sun. You become the sunlight. End of round six. End of round six.", "segments": [{"id": 0, "seek": 0, "start": 3.4200000000000004, "end": 12.42, "text": " Welcome to the three-minute guided meditation training by All Here.", "tokens": [50364, 4027, 281, 264, 1045, 12, 18256, 19663, 12537, 3097, 538, 439, 510, 13, 50984], "temperature": 0, "avg_logprob": -0.5662485010483685, "compression_ratio": 0.9852941176470589, "no_speech_prob": 0.02618488296866417, "words": [{"word": " Welcome", "start": 3.4200000000000004, "end": 4.82, "probability": 0.7245187163352966}, {"word": " to", "start": 4.82, "end": 5.7, "probability": 0.9475346803665161}, {"word": " the", "start": 5.7, "end": 5.84, "probability": 0.9425530433654785}, {"word": " three", "start": 5.84, "end": 6.16, "probability": 0.46705061197280884}, {"word": "-minute", "start": 6.16, "end": 6.42, "probability": 0.786159336566925}, {"word": " guided", "start": 6.42, "end": 8.18, "probability": 0.9783556461334229}, {"word": " meditation", "start": 8.18, "end": 9, "probability": 0.9332318305969238}, {"word": " training", "start": 9, "end": 9.82, "probability": 0.9875624179840088}, {"word": " by", "start": 9.82, "